rows.label: tlk70000041_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Most of the stuff that was
in this warehouse has been
moved to the shelter.

rows.label: tlk70000041_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Which means it's bye-bye to this old
place and my job guarding it...

rows.label: tlk70000041_01_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm s'posed to be reassigned to a
completely different division, but it's
gonna be hard to part with this job.

rows.label: tlk70000041_01_msg0004
rows.name:
It's funny, y'know? I was always
complaining about how boring this job
was, and now I don't want to leave...
